op|\n* Mike Score \u2013 lead vocals, keyboards\n* Joe Rodriguez \u2013 lead guitar\n* Michael Brahm \u2013 drums\n*Albert Cruz \u2013 drums (till 2006)\n* Pando \u2013 bass guitar\n*Robbie Hanson \u2013 bass guitar (till 2006)\n|valign=top|\n* Mike Score \u2013 lead vocals, keyboards\n* Joe Rodriguez \u2013 lead guitar\n* Pando \u2013 bass guitar\n* Kevin Rankin \u2013 drums\n|valign=top|\n* Mike Score \u2013 lead vocals, keyboards\n* Pando \u2013 bass guitar\n* Kevin Rankin \u2013 drums\n* Gord Deppe \u2013 lead guitar\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n{{main|A Flock of Seagulls discography}}\n*''[[A Flock of Seagulls (album)|A Flock of Seagulls]]'' (1982)\n*''[[Listen (A Flock of Seagulls album)|Listen]]'' (1983)\n*''[[The Story of a Young Heart]]'' (1984)\n*''[[Dream Come True (A Flock of Seagulls album)|Dream Come True]]'' (1986)\n*''[[The Light at the End of the World (A Flock of Seagulls album)|The Light at the End of the World]]'' (1995)\n*''[[Ascension (A Flock of Seagulls album)|Ascension]]'' (2018)\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of bands named after other performers' songs]]\n*[[List of new wave artists and bands]]\n*[[List of Peel sessions]]\n*[[List of synth-pop artists]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.aflockofseagulls.org/ A Flock of Seagulls' Official website]\n*[http://www.mikescore.com/ Mike Score's Official website]\n\n{{A Flock of Seagulls}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Flock of Seagulls, A}}\n[[Category:1979 establishments in England]]\n[[Category:1986 disestablishments in England]]\n[[Category:1989 establishments in England]]\n[[Category:English new wave musical groups]]\n[[Category:British synth-pop new wave groups]]\n[[Category:Grammy Award winners]]\n[[Category:Musical groups disestablished in 1986]]\n[[Category:Musical groups established in 1979]]\n[[Category:Musical groups from Liverpool]]\n[[Category:Musical groups reestablished in 1989]]\n[[Category:A Flock of Seagulls| ]]\n", "name_user": "Bahiagrass",