e people of Bhatni speak [[Bhojpuri]] and [[Hindi]], although English is increasingly used by younger people of the area.\n\n==Education==\nTwo private colleges offer degrees: \u0936\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0938\u093f\u0926\u094d\u0927\u0947\u0936\u094d\u0935\u0930 \u0936\u0940\u0924\u0932\u0926\u0947\u0935 \u0928\u093e\u0930\u093e\u092f\u0923 \u092e\u0939\u093e\u0935\u093f\u0926\u094d\u092f\u093e\u0932\u092f and \u0936\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u092c\u091a\u094d\u091a\u0928 \u0921\u0949\u0915\u094d\u091f\u0930 \u092d\u0940\u092e\u0930\u093e\u0935 \u0905\u0902\u092c\u0947\u0921\u0915\u0930 \u0907\u0902\u091f\u0930 \u0915\u0949\u0932\u0947\u091c (affiliated to D.D.U. Gorakhpur University). Subhash Intermediate College is in the heart of the city. It is one of the oldest colleges in a radius of 1.5 km. A government Junior High School is located in ..bharhe chaura\n\n==Politics==\nBoth Behradaber and gram Panchayat have often been in the limelight for the politics . Pandey chauraha has seen much development since it was awarded the same status as Gram Panchayat behradaber..1 jaiprkash pandey 2.Hari prkash Pandey 3.Nanlal pandey 4.Subhash Chandra Pandey. By open Pandey chauraha 2000..... \n\nOnly B.J.P.... \u092d\u093e\u0930\u0924\u0940\u092f \u091c\u0928\u0924\u093e \u092a\u093e\u0930\u094d\u091f\u0940  \n\n==References==\n1.Census of india 2000; including cities ,villages and Pandey chauraha....(provisional ) {{Deoria district}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Deoria district]]\n", "name_user": "2405:204:a288:d2fe::2355:80b1", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bhatni_Bazar"}
