arliament-5251042/ |title=Kumar Sanu and Anuradha Paudwal honoured at UK Houses of Parliament |date=8 July 2018 |publisher= |accessdate=26 October 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Filmfare Awards===\n;Won\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Song\n! Film\n! Music director(s)\n! Lyricist\n|-\n|1990\n|\"Ab Tere Bin\"\n|''[[Aashiqui]]''\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Nadeem-Shravan]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Sameer (lyricist)|Sameer]]\n|-\n|1991\n|\"Mera Dil Bhi Kitna Pagal Hai\"\n|''[[Saajan]]''\n|-\n|1992\n|\"Sochenge Tumhe Pyaar\"\n|''[[Deewana (1992 film)|Deewana]]''\n|-\n|1993\n|\"Yeh Kaali Kaali Aankhen\"\n|''[[Baazigar]]''\n|[[Anu Malik]]\n| [[Dev Kohli]]\n|-\n|1994\n|\"Ek Ladki Ko Dekha\"\n|''[[1942: A Love Story]]''\n|[[R.D. Burman]]\n|[[Javed Akhtar]]\n|}\n\n;Nominated\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Song\n! Film\n|-\n| 1993\n| \"Baazigar O Baazigar\"\n| ''[[Baazigar]]''\n|-\n|-\n| 1994\n| \"Kuch Na Kaho\"\n| ''[[1942: A Love Story]]''\n|-\n| 1995\n| \"Tujhe Dekha To\"\n| ''[[Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge]]''\n|-\n|-\n| 1995\n| \"Tu Mile Dil Khile\"\n| ''[[Criminal (1995 film)#Hindi Version]]''\n|-\n| 1997\n| \"Do Dil Mil Rahe Hain\"\n| ''[[Pardes (film)|Pardes]]''\n|-\n| 1998\n| \"Ladki Badi Anjaani Hai\"\n| ''[[Kuch Kuch Hota Hai]]''\n|-\n| 1999\n| \"Aankhon Ki Gusthakiyaan\"\n| ''[[Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam]]''\n|-\n| 2003\n| \"Sanam Mere Humraaz\"\n| ''[[Humraaz]]''\n|-\n| 2003\n| \"Kisise Tum Pyar Karo\"\n| ''[[Andaaz]]''\n|}\n\n===Other awards===\n* 2016: 8th position on \"Google most searched Indian singers in last 10 years\"<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/salman-khan-sunny-leone-google-most-searched-actors-2915875/ |title=Salman Khan, Sunny Leone are Google's most searched Indian actors of last 10 years |date=15 July 2016 |access-date=29 July 2016}}</ref>\n* 2003: Bollywood Music Award For \"Best Artist of the Decade\"\n* 2001: Channel V Award For Best Male Playback for \"Chand Sitare\" - ''[[Kaho Naa... Pyaar Hai